long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Download AliExpress product images and videos easily with this popular tool!
Click once to save AliExpress images in high quality directly to your computer. Simple and efficient!

⭐ **Getting Started:**

🚀 Click "Add to Chrome" to install the extension.
🛍️ Open your target AliExpress product page.
📸 Click on the AliExpress Image Downloader icon to open it.
📥 Download product images by variants, main, and description.
📊 Export images and video details to Excel.

⭐ **Features:**

❤️free
🗂️ Download Single Images (*.jpeg)

💎pro
🖼️ One Click Download Images (*.zip,*.xlsx)
🎥 Download Videos (*.mp4)

❓ **Why Choose AliExpress Image Downloader?**

⚡ Fast and easy way to download AliExpress product images and videos.
📝 Export product information including goodsId,goodsName, variantName, price, and URLs directly to Excel.
📈 Perfect for sellers, researchers, and anyone needing to save product details from AliExpress.
